Discipline. Patience. Courage.These are the hallmarks of the successful long-term investor—and the traits that we feel set Roberts Glore apart.Discipline.In an increasingly complex and globalized financial marketplace, information is plentiful—but wisdom is rare.Courage.Since 1984, our team of portfolio managers has successfully navigated booms and busts in the financial markets with a steady focus on long-term value creation.Patience.We invest with the long term in view. We weigh success not over months or quarters, but over many years—and even decades. 



















